snippet.textDisplay:
inconsistency is one of the biggest problem that needs to be solved. The problem starts with midfielder who is daring enough to unlock opposition defence. unlike top team where they have consistency on back four and midfielder, we do not. So far Pogba has not be able to cement his place yet the nature of league requires players to maintain performance.
This creates problem for the forward, i am pretty impressed with Ole on shooting conversion, unfortunately, we have only one way to play. switch sides, one two, and run the channels. therefore if teams play defensive, compact defense is way to go.
like ole said, next year play is based on today experiment. i hope he gets the players he likes.
